data.description:
IN TOWN AND CLOSE TO THE COVE!!! This 2bed 1 bath home is only a few blocks from beautiful Lake Eufaula.
 Bring your bags and start enjoying everything Eufaula has to offer. This home has been remodeled and has a new roof, all new appliances that stay with the home. Great short-term rental or make it your forever home. This home sits on a large corner lot with a chain-link fence yard, also a nice size shed to store your toys. Don't let this slip past you! Come take a look and see for yourself! Call today for a viewing of this amazing little gem!!!
